Package ru.nsu.fit.tretyakov.operators

Class Number

java.lang.Object
ru.nsu.fit.tretyakov.operators.Number
All Implemented Interfaces:
Operator
public class Number extends Object implements Operator
This class is the boxing of the complex number. It contains imagine and real parts of the complex number and allows user to make some real and operations above this number.
